{"tid":2370450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人由細到大都唔識點樣回應客套說話？","createTime":"2021-01-18T04:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T05:23:22.000Z","uid":359634,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4fb31b9b163ffedaab76631546b9b40c114b84e4","tid":2370450,"uid":359634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:56:24.000Z","msg":"細個嗰時又內向又有少少自我中心，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以完全唔識點樣回應人哋啲客套說話，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如去探遠房親戚嗰時，佢哋會講：<br />\n「你又高咗喎」<br />\n「大個咗喎」<br />\n「個樣唔同喎」<br />\n「你件衫好好睇喎」<br />\n但係細個嗰時唔知點解對呢啲說話完全冇感覺，唔係太知點應，然後啲親戚見到我唔講嘢又唔知講咩好，搞到好似好尷尬，搞到阿爸阿媽成日要幫我打圓場。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係而家就算大過咗我通常都唔會主動講呢啲客套說話，亦都唔係太識點應，就算人哋講先嘅話我都淨係笑一笑，答句「係呀」就算，然後冷場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人都係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9089ac9630d61c72b052842a298cd90769049094","tid":2370450,"uid":359634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:57:01.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"9860d9cc28744706c94fe45ea2f201b49faf7978","tid":2370450,"uid":359634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:57:12.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"8ee3da2f8a64376feeeefa0d4744a11f03ea36dd","tid":2370450,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:57:39.000Z","msg":"駁佢地嘴就得"},{"pid":"0f3cb0111d3e16b43e949f1a91a3bccc4ed7cacb","tid":2370450,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:58:08.000Z","msg":"答係咩 係呀 哈哈咪得"},{"pid":"d4bcc4c588ae8c42e132ae29aea683327412088b","tid":2370450,"uid":123151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:58:11.000Z","msg":"講句「多謝」囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a60f087f3c3a4dcc7897f81200bbde21afd875c","tid":2370450,"uid":65439